# random integer generator

# not useful anymore :  use the irandom node instead

@ in clock
@ in min
@ in max

@ out out

+ random rnd
> _in_@clock rnd@clock

+ map scale
= 0 scale@imin
= 1 scale@imax
> _in_@min scale@omin
> _in_@max scale@omax
> rnd@out scale@in

+ round rti
> scale@out rti@in

> rti@out _out_@out

